Author: big_hoop_attitude
Text: Oddly, Google says power walking is 200 calories/hour. When I halved soccer it was only 180, lol.   The only difference between power walking and serving is when serving it's not just cardio; You use arms, core, etc. because you're always carrying, wiping, etc.
